          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-1-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-1-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bacon lardons are cooking, peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lardons are crispy, transfer them to a plate and return the pan (and oil!) to a medium heat</p><p>Add the<strong> diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until softened</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> and <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[160ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
