          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-42-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked spaghetti</strong> and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2084.-step-5-x200.jpg",
